      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through method of manufactured solutions or equivalent. Required level 1 for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has published MMS verification results for incompressible Navier-Stokes with rotating reference frames. Order-of-accuracy confirmed at 1.97 for velocity components. Achieved level 2."
