      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD analyst must have documented training and experience with rotating machinery simulations. Independent review of model setup required. Required level 1.",
      "rationale": "Lead analyst has 8 years experience with CFD hemolysis modeling and completed ANSYS turbomachinery training. Model setup independently reviewed by senior engineer. Boundary condition specification checked against published FDA protocol. Use error risk assessed as low."
    },
    {
