      "rationale": "Model form assessment not required at MRL 2 for this application. SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature consensus for centrifugal pump hemolysis. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al.) applied consistently with FDA guidance. Factor scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements."
    },
