    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Validation results demonstrate CFD predictions within experimental uncertainty at all five operating points (MARE 8.7%). UQ campaign across 128 dimensional tolerance samples confirms RH < 1 acceptance criterion satisfied throughout the design space. Discretization error (GCI max 3.2%) and iterative convergence verified. The model is assessed as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
